Philip Rhoden, director of Clubfinance, said: "We have had calls from frustrated investors who invested directly through the Royal Mail share offer website and have been unable to sell their shares as soon as they would have liked, either because they have been waiting for their paper share certificate to arrive or having had difficulty dealing through Equiniti."
